# Python

- Run via `uv run` / `make`; deps in `pyproject.toml`.
- `make format` before commit if touching Python.
- Type hints on public functions; mypy strict on `pdiseg/`.
- Tests in `tests/` mirror CLI and pipeline contracts.
- Minimal scope: no unrelated refactors in the same diff.

Coverage gate: 80% on `pdiseg/` (`make test`).
